{"tid":1888843,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[東瀛] 暑假去青森、岩手嘅話有咩景點特别推薦？","createTime":"2020-02-20T12:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T11:20:18.000Z","uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"39ecdeb98bd0d6479524ab729851cdc0ce3e1005","tid":1888843,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:20:43.000Z","msg":"請教一下各位遊日達人暑假去<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">青森、岩手</span>嘅話有咩景點特别推薦？<br />\n<br />\n今次旅程預計會同大學啲同學去<br />\n因為想去啲大家都未去過嘅東瀛城市<br />\n所以揀咗呢兩個縣做擬定嘅目的地<br />\n<br />\n因為預計畢業咗之後冇機會再一齊旅行<br />\n所以想去一啲啱年輕人嘅景點<br />\n同玩一啲學生時期之後好難再玩、做到嘅嘢 (eg露營、水上活動&hellip;&hellip;)<br />\n而因為勁大機會係最後一次咁齊人去旅行，我哋<span style=\"color: purple;\">預算會高少少，負擔到一啲可能貴少少嘅活動</span><br />\n<br />\n請各位遊日達人<span style=\"color: brown;\">不吝賜教</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97697bf4751de49d0cbee747357066d8284e3f75","tid":1888843,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"自駕定jr 有d地方好偏未必去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />青森要去浸不老不死黃金溫泉 無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7babfdd0cffe4e8aac5e30a6d4b87b9ff0b7df80","tid":1888843,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97697bf4751de49d0cbee747357066d8284e3f75","tid":1888843,"uid":26766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:22:23.000Z","msg":"自駕定jr 有d地方好偏未必去到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />青森要去浸不老不死黃金溫泉 無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T12:24:43.000Z","msg":"我哋冇人有車牌，未check但怕租車會好貴 (想預返多啲$去食同玩度)<br />\n所以應該會坐公共交通工具<br />\n諗緊買JR Pass"},{"pid":"b76fcced304d7b7f4be2c496d8c67d95125a1e7e","tid":1888843,"uid":258706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"qu